        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 19. Mitra gonatophora Sturany, 1903, Station 48 (Yanbu' al Bahr, Saudi Arabia, Red Sea). A-G. Figured syntype, NHMW 84210: front (A-B), right side (C-D), back (E), protoconch (F-G). H-K. Syntype, NHMW 84211: protoconch (H), front (I), right side (J), back (K). L. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-E, I-K: 1 mm, F-H: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 30. Mangelia epicharis Sturany, 1903, Locality 16 (Jazirat Shakir, Egypt, Red Sea). A-D, F, H. Holotype, NHMW 37714: front (A-B), right side (C), back (D), microsculpture (F), protoconch (H). E. Original figure by Sturany (1903). G. Original holotype label. Scale bars: A-D: 0.5 mm, F: 0.2 mm, H: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118658" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118678" .

